```plantuml
@startuml Sanperolo_The-Intelligent-Bike

actor User
participant "Frontend (Angular)" as Frontend
participant "Backend API (Django)" as Backend
participant "MQTT Broker" as MQTT
participant "Hardware (Sensors)" as Hardware
participant "Database (PostgreSQL)" as Database

User -> Frontend: Accesses dashboard
Frontend -> Backend: GET /api/sensor-data
Backend -> Database: Query sensor data
Database --> Backend: Return sensor data
Backend --> Frontend: Return JSON response
Frontend -> User: Display data visualizations

Hardware -> MQTT: Publish sensor data (topic: bike/sensors)
MQTT -> Backend: Subscribe to bike/sensors
Backend -> Database: Save sensor data
Database --> Backend: Confirm save

@enduml
```